`timescale 1ns/1ps

// AUTO-GENERATED by sim/tools/gen_tb_top.py
// Topology: mesh_2x1  (2x1, num_vc=1)
// DO NOT EDIT - modify the generator or sim/topologies/*.yaml instead.
//
// 2 nodes live inside noc_fabric_mesh_2x1 (NMU + REQ/RSP router + NSU per
// node, joined by directional links). tb_top creates the DPI handles, drives
// each node's master-side AXI with a test master_wrap, ejects each node's
// slave-side AXI with a test slave_wrap, and owns the scoreboard exit logic.
// Variant->instance pairing: master at node k is fed node (k+1)'s coordinate
// scenario, so traffic crosses the fabric to node (k+1) and ejects there.
//
// Self-clocked: clk_i/rst_ni are internal logic (10 ns clock, 4-cycle reset).
// Plusargs +scenario_node0=<path> ... +scenario_node1=<path> kick off the run.

`ifndef TB_TOP_SV
